stories.text:
Yeah :)

No idea what this page is for and why Chrome offers it.

But if you go to chrome://device-log it shows a lot of information about your USB devices. Names, vendoes, GUIDs etc.

And a log of what they have been doing (since boot?)

Why is this part of a browser?
